ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.datatype

Class CE

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractType
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractComposite
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v23.datatype.CE
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Composite, Type, Visitable, Serializable

    public class CE
extends AbstractComposite

    Represents an HL7 CE (coded element) data type. This type consists of the following components:

    • identifier (ID)
    • text (ST)
    • name of coding system (ST)
    • alternate identifier (ID)
    • alternate text (ST)
    • name of alternate coding system (ST)
